# Changelog Innoship

## [1.3.8]
    - Fix compatibility with Amasty_Checkout => billing city display none for multiple payment methods

## [1.3.7]
    - Fix compatibility with Amasty_Checkout => automatically refresh payment methods based on shipping method selection

## [1.3.6]
    - Fix compatibility with Amasty_Checkout
    - Fix return on bin/magento innoship:dataimport
    - Fix selecting city and region based in map interface

## [1.3.5]
    - Fix compatibility with Amasty_Checkout

## [1.3.4]
    - Compatibility with PHP 8.4

## [1.3.3]
    - Fix import address without ","
    - Important
        - After install run bin/magento innoship:dataimport

## [1.3.2]
    - Add city selection to customer account address book

## [1.3.1]
    - Fix addresses from InnoShip API
    - Fix region error in checkout for logged in users

## [1.3]
    - Enable translations on map via JS
    - Country Specific Fees
    - Automatic determine serviceID for InnoShip
    - New console command innoship:regioimport
        - Example: bin/magento innoship:regioimport PL
    - Fix when loker is still present in order and order was not send with locker. (only for new customer with Amasty Shipping Restrictions)
    - Automatic pricing when "Show Courier List" is enable
        - It is based on "Multiplicator Pret" and "Automatic Price" => "Yes"
    - Locker map => drag / zoom => getting all lockers for a 5km radious
    - Security improvements
    - Performance improvements
    - Important
        - After install run bin/magento innoship:dataimport
        - After install run bin/magento innoship:externalid


## [1.2]
    - Fixes for PHP 8.2
    - Fixes for Magento 2.4.7
    - Fix min 1 KG when creating AWB
    - Fix display information for Locker not in the DB in Admin
    - Fix display information for Locker not in the DB in Frontend Client account
    - Fix when creating AWB from Admin, if locker does not exist in DB, it will not allow AWB generation
    - Fix logged in customer shipping address phone bug from Magento 2.4.7
    - Fix shipping cost calculation for functionality Create Admin Order
    - Fix get locker list when courier is not in Magento database
    - Add patch to rename "Satu-Mare" to "Satu Mare" in Magento database
    - AWB label print will generate a PDF file on the fly and download it. (Please delete folder /pub/media/innoship/)
    - Feature: Add option to use GPS location to idenfity lockers around me
    - Feature: Favorite Locker functionality for logged in customers

